oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:title: Frontier Attractions: Grand Ole Opry Units Version 2
oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:subject: Frontier Attractions; Grand ole opry (Radio program); Offset printing;
oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:description: A black and white negative taped to and framed by a masking sheet advertising the Grand Ole Opry stars available through Frontier Attractions. The negative features photographs of Ernest Tubb, Minnie Pearl, Loretta Lynn, the Willis Brothers, and others. Some of the negatives that would have contained Frontier Attraction's name and address have been cut out and are missing. The masking sheet also contains Hatch Show Print's address taped to it. The negative would have been used to create a corresponding printing plate.
